{"type":"text","timestamp":1773351572132,"sessionID":"ses_31c036dc4ffejmXOCp5uBNFg7f","part":{"id":"prt_ce3fd756f002UA1PN2WXrzuMkn","sessionID":"ses_31c036dc4ffejmXOCp5uBNFg7f","messageID":"msg_ce3fd6d94001u04hrqW7oBL1eL","type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the codebase. Let me implement the portless integration. Here's my approach:\n\n1. **Config**: Add `portless` config section to `WomboConfig` for enabling/disabling and proxy settings\n2. **New module `src/lib/portless.ts`**: Utility functions for portless integration (checking availability, generating environment variables, wrapping commands)\n3. **Launcher integration**: Inject portless environment into agent spawning so any server the agent starts uses portless\n4. **Worktree integration**: Set up portless awareness in worktrees\n5. **Prompt integration**: Inform agents to use portless for any server commands\n6. **Init integration**: Add portless config to init flow\n\nLet me start:","time":{"start":1773351572132,"end":1773351572132}}}
